Time":"2020-02-25T04:44:08.000Z","msg":"孔子係講緊連對武王伐紂（先唔當呢樣野係歷史上嘅政治鬥爭，當左佢係最簡單嘅討伐暴政。孔子自己其實都對呢樣野頗有微言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你話呢種人唔會支持霸權暴政，但係都唔會支持你反抗"},{"pid":"b87e8e1d7087a09db8500e03a98c6b4232d0138a","tid":1896221,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T04:54:46.000Z","msg":"真係好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 孔子都俾共產黨批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WcBktkZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWcBktkZ.jpg&h=ee9e8e93&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"760462558d4a3fe0e4c1fb669b1140e357805981","tid":1896221,"uid":239392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T05:04:52.000Z","msg":"黑警連耶穌都照打，怕你孔子有牙？"},{"pid":"f145539981bea8268b8f41602ee8e775e40b3e45","tid":1896221,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T11:07:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e67834e6f0936dd967a5db5d1347560a3c5c40fa","tid":1896221,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T11:08:21.000Z","msg":"老而不死 是為賊也"}]}